1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 3=

4
00:00:25,719 --> 00:00:26,519
You...

5
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:31,679
How could you
break my Heaven-Burning Art?

6
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:33,799
Some people won't listen
until they're on the brink of death.

7
00:00:34,119 --> 00:00:36,759
Think about it on your way
to the afterlife, ugly freak.

8
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:39,520
What?

9
00:00:40,039 --> 00:00:42,920
His cultivation level actually broke
through the fifth rank in an instant.

10
00:00:43,240 --> 00:00:45,079
For ordinary warriors to advance a rank,

11
00:00:45,159 --> 00:00:46,960
it takes at least three to five years.

12
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:49,719
He's just an unranked saberman.

13
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:51,560
How could one slash
break through a rank?

14
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:53,479
Have you ever heard of anyone

15
00:00:53,679 --> 00:00:55,079
who could break through
a rank with one slash?

16
00:00:55,679 --> 00:00:57,840
Aside from grandmasters
with Heavenly Spirit Roots,

17
00:00:58,159 --> 00:01:00,159
I've never heard of anyone
who could do it.

18
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:04,280
Could his innate talent
rival that of a grandmaster?

19
00:01:05,319 --> 00:01:07,400
Looks like you'll have to eat your hat.

20
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:07,920
I...

21
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:14,280
Oh, that was close.
I almost lost my life.

22
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:17,280
(But just now...)

23
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:20,159
(Why did I feel a strange power
surging through my body?)

24
00:01:20,799 --> 00:01:23,840
(Could my cultivation level
have improved again?)

25
00:01:39,879 --> 00:01:42,560
I thought you were a goner.

26
00:01:46,719 --> 00:01:47,200
Miss.

27
00:01:47,719 --> 00:01:50,719
I'm Fang Xiaojiu.
Thank you for saving my life.

28
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,879
Miss Fang, there's no need for that.

29
00:01:52,959 --> 00:01:54,120
It was nothing.

30
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:55,359
To defeat the Demon Sect's

31
00:01:55,359 --> 00:01:57,239
Northern Evil Duo all by yourself,

32
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:59,200
you truly have remarkable skills.

33
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,439
Since you two arrived long ago,

34
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,159
why only show yourselves now?

35
00:02:10,439 --> 00:02:11,840
You knew we were here?

36
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,000
I was just guessing.

37
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:15,360
But judging by your reactions,

38
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:16,919
I guessed right.

39
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,360
Shameless.

40
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,400
Young man, your battle just now

41
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:22,599
was truly astonishing.

42
00:02:22,599 --> 00:02:23,960
It was truly a sight to behold.

43
00:02:25,719 --> 00:02:27,479
The Demon Sect is wreaking havoc
across the martial world,

44
00:02:27,759 --> 00:02:29,280
leaving countless people to suffer.

45
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:33,680
Would you be willing
to join forces with the Wudu Sect

46
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,719
to eliminate the Demon Sect

47
00:02:35,199 --> 00:02:36,800
and protect the people?

48
00:02:38,319 --> 00:02:39,719
My master ordered me
to return to my sect

49
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,240
and report back.

50
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:42,560
Miss,

51
00:02:42,919 --> 00:02:43,719
I'm afraid I can't help you.

52
00:02:44,879 --> 00:02:45,479
I see.

53
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:48,560
You're just afraid of being outdone
and making yourself look bad.

54
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:50,280
Xiao, don't be rude.

55
00:02:53,159 --> 00:02:54,879
Young man, since you have other plans,

56
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,400
I won't force you.

57
00:02:58,120 --> 00:03:00,759
I'm Duan Qingyao.
I'll be staying in Gusu for a few days.

58
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,520
If you change your mind,

59
00:03:03,599 --> 00:03:04,800
you can come find me anytime.

60
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,719
What are you doing? Get up.

61
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:40,759
The Demon Sect killed my parents.

62
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,599
Not only did you save my life,

63
00:03:42,599 --> 00:03:44,159
but you also avenged my family.

64
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:46,120
If you don't mind,

65
00:03:46,199 --> 00:03:47,680
I wish to serve by your side

66
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,479
as your maid

67
00:03:48,479 --> 00:03:49,479
to repay your kindness.

68
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:57,199
You don't want me?

69
00:04:00,159 --> 00:04:04,400
Or do you think I'm too ugly

70
00:04:05,439 --> 00:04:06,599
and too unrefined?

71
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,039
No, no.

72
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:11,800
Miss, do you have some misunderstanding
about what ugly means?

73
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,199
If you're considered ugly,

74
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:15,319
then my master
will be seen as a monster.

75
00:04:27,079 --> 00:04:28,920
So you agree?

76
00:04:29,079 --> 00:04:30,720
(After I break off my engagement
with the Murong family,)

77
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,839
(I'll help her find a good life.)

78
00:04:34,439 --> 00:04:36,480
Miss Fang, get up first.

79
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:38,959
From now on,

80
00:04:39,439 --> 00:04:40,800
you can just

81
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,800
call me Dasheng.

82
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:43,360
Dasheng.

83
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:45,040
Then you can call me Xiaojiu.

84
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:45,959
Xiaojiu.

85
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:54,759
Oh, you've got dirt on your face.

86
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:20,140
♪One thought pulls me in, the mortal
world becomes the battlefield♪

87
00:05:21,300 --> 00:05:26,380
♪Who traded true love
for a body covered in scars?♪

88
00:05:27,700 --> 00:05:33,820
♪The lanterns still burn,
but the vows have grown cold♪

89
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,199
Miss,

90
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:39,439
you really let Peng Dasheng go?

91
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:40,920
Of course not.

92
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:43,560
Anyone the Wudu Sect wants

93
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,360
will never slip away so easily.

94
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:48,120
There are countless heroes
in the martial world.

95
00:05:48,439 --> 00:05:49,439
Why waste our time on someone

96
00:05:49,439 --> 00:05:51,879
who doesn't even have inner force?

97
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,360
There are many experts
in the martial world.

98
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:57,959
But only a handful
can truly become our allies.

99
00:05:58,879 --> 00:06:00,800
If he had agreed today,

100
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,399
I might have thought less of him.

101
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:04,120
But he refused.

102
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:09,040
I think he just doesn't know
what's good for him.

103
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,839
Keep someone watching him.

104
00:06:10,959 --> 00:06:13,240
I want to know his every move in Gusu.

105
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,160
Yes.

106
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:19,540
♪You traded your whole life
for my promise never to regret♪

107
00:06:20,100 --> 00:06:22,100
♪If this martial world...♪

108
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:30,879
Dasheng,

109
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:34,319
what kind of medicine
are you hiding in that gourd?

110
00:06:34,639 --> 00:06:36,199
It's my lifesaver.

111
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,000
Lifesaver?

112
00:06:39,439 --> 00:06:40,000
Yes.

113
00:06:40,639 --> 00:06:42,279
My master said
I was born with sealed meridians.

114
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:43,360
I was destined to live a short life.

115
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:45,759
All these years, my master's pills

116
00:06:45,759 --> 00:06:46,879
are the only thing keeping me alive.

117
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:49,120
That's why I call them my lifesaver.

118
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:52,319
What happens when the pills runs out?

119
00:06:54,839 --> 00:06:56,399
Then I'll die.

120
00:06:58,759 --> 00:06:59,600
Then...

121
00:07:01,759 --> 00:07:02,639
I'm just kidding.

122
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:03,680
My master said

123
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,680
as long as I return
to my sect within a month,

124
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,800
everything will be fine.

125
00:07:07,519 --> 00:07:08,639
Don't worry, Dasheng.

126
00:07:08,639 --> 00:07:11,120
Xiaojiu will scour the land
for the best healers.

127
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,759
Someone's bound to cure you.

128
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,040
Silly girl.

129
00:07:16,199 --> 00:07:17,199
This isn't an illness.

130
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:18,199
It's the hand I was dealt.

131
00:07:18,959 --> 00:07:20,120
But what about you, Xiaojiu?

132
00:07:20,319 --> 00:07:21,680
Your enemy is dead.

133
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,639
Your revenge is complete.

134
00:07:22,639 --> 00:07:23,839
What do you plan to do next?

135
00:07:28,879 --> 00:07:30,800
Of course I'll stay with you, Dasheng.

136
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:33,120
Wherever you go, I go.

137
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:38,000
(This girl just lost her family.)

138
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:41,000
(She probably sees me
as her only support now.)

139
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,680
(But my own life
could end at any moment.)

140
00:07:43,959 --> 00:07:44,959
(How can I protect her?)

141
00:07:44,959 --> 00:07:46,040
Oh right, Dasheng.

142
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:48,879
You said you were going to Murong Manor
to break off your engagement.

143
00:07:49,079 --> 00:07:51,120
But you grew up training at your sect.

144
00:07:51,279 --> 00:07:53,319
How did you end up with a marriage
arrangement with Miss Murong?

145
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:56,040
That's a long story.

146
00:07:56,319 --> 00:07:57,319
Back then,

147
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,560
my master saved the life
of the Murong family's head.

148
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:02,120
To repay him, Mr. Murong

149
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:04,199
arranged a marriage between me
and the Murong family's daughter.

150
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,319
But now the Murong family head's
has passed away,

151
00:08:06,439 --> 00:08:07,800
and I can't leave my sect.

152
00:08:08,079 --> 00:08:10,920
So this time,
my master sent me down the mountain

153
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,199
to end this engagement.

154
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:17,759
Young man,
you'll be making a wasted trip.

155
00:08:18,319 --> 00:08:19,839
Sir, what do you mean?

156
00:08:20,079 --> 00:08:21,279
(Fortune Teller)
Fortune-telling.

157
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:22,759
Ten coins per reading

158
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,519
Now can you tell me?

159
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:38,360
Well, I'll tell you the truth.

160
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:41,519
Ten days ago, the Murong family's head
announced a martial competition

161
00:08:41,519 --> 00:08:45,080
to choose a husband
for his daughter, Murong Bingqing.

162
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,960
The news spread quickly,

163
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:49,639
and young talents
from all over the martial world

164
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:50,879
flocked to Gusu,

165
00:08:50,879 --> 00:08:52,720
all eager for a chance.

166
00:08:53,399 --> 00:08:55,120
Isn't it just a martial competition
to find a husband?

167
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,840
Why make such a fuss?

168
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,960
Young lady,
you don't know the whole story.

169
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,960
Murong Xiang,
the head of the Murong family,

170
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:04,080
is the Leader
of the Martial Arts Alliance.

171
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:06,960
Murong Bingqing is his only daughter.

172
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:07,960
Think about it.

173
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,799
Whoever marries into the Murong family

174
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:12,679
can inherit the entire family fortune.

175
00:09:12,879 --> 00:09:13,679
And besides,

176
00:09:13,799 --> 00:09:16,480
rumor has it that Murong Bingqing
is unmatched in beauty.

177
00:09:16,679 --> 00:09:21,080
A daughter like her
would have suitors everywhere.

178
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:24,080
Then what did you mean when you said
I'd be making a wasted trip?

179
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:25,440
To show his appreciation,

180
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,240
today,

181
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,960
Murong Xiang is
hosting a banquet at Yanziji Tavern

182
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:30,559
for young talents
from across the martial world.

183
00:09:30,639 --> 00:09:32,919
Young man,
if you're not on the guest list,

184
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:34,559
you won't even get through the door.

185
00:09:34,559 --> 00:09:36,960
Wouldn't that make
your trip for nothing?

186
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:39,600
Now that you mention it,

187
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,320
I want to see it even more.

188
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:43,000
Xiaojiu, let's go.

189
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:49,680
(Fortune Teller)

190
00:09:55,980 --> 00:09:59,620
(Tang Changsheng,
Leader of the Shuzhong Tang Clan)

191
00:10:03,159 --> 00:10:05,480
I'm Peng Dasheng.
I'd like to see your family head.

192
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,840
Please inform him.

193
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,879
You? A poor guy like you

194
00:10:12,879 --> 00:10:14,519
wants to see our family head?

195
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:19,440
Do you even know your place?

196
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,639
You think you're worthy?

197
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:26,159
How can you talk to people like that?

198
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:27,279
You look down on everyone.

199
00:10:27,380 --> 00:10:27,920
Woof! Woof!

200
00:10:29,399 --> 00:10:30,840
You little brat.

201
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:31,639
You're asking for a beating.

202
00:10:34,519 --> 00:10:35,840
You filthy beggar.

203
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,759
Trying to play the hero
and save the beauty?

204
00:10:37,759 --> 00:10:38,840
With those skills?

205
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:39,960
Watch your mouth.

206
00:10:40,039 --> 00:10:41,120
Apologize to her.

207
00:10:43,399 --> 00:10:44,240
I'm... so... sorry!

208
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:45,720
I'm sorry.

209
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:46,519
I'm so sorry.

210
00:10:46,679 --> 00:10:48,159
Be sincere.

211
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:54,759
I was wrong. I'm sorry.

212
00:10:54,759 --> 00:10:57,039
That's not enough.

213
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:06,240
I'm shameless. I'm a scoundrel.

214
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,919
I looked down on people.

215
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:11,240
Miss, please forgive me. I beg you.

216
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:19,559
How dare you cause trouble
in front of Murong Manor?

217
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,480
You've got some nerve.

218
00:11:40,540 --> 00:11:41,020
♪Come on♪

219
00:11:44,540 --> 00:11:46,220
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

220
00:11:48,180 --> 00:11:51,140
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

221
00:11:51,420 --> 00:11:54,340
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

222
00:11:54,580 --> 00:11:57,420
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

223
00:11:57,820 --> 00:12:00,420
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

224
00:12:00,940 --> 00:12:03,900
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

225
00:12:04,140 --> 00:12:07,140
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

226
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:10,220
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

227
00:12:10,380 --> 00:12:13,140
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

228
00:12:13,700 --> 00:12:17,020
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

229
00:12:17,060 --> 00:12:20,060
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

230
00:12:20,100 --> 00:12:25,740
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

231
00:12:26,140 --> 00:12:28,180
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

232
00:12:28,740 --> 00:12:31,260
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

233
00:12:31,980 --> 00:12:34,380
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

234
00:12:34,500 --> 00:12:38,180
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

235
00:12:38,780 --> 00:12:41,380
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

236
00:12:41,820 --> 00:12:43,940
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

237
00:12:44,100 --> 00:12:47,380
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

238
00:12:47,420 --> 00:12:51,700
♪I am my own king♪

239
00:13:04,780 --> 00:13:06,140
♪I emerge into the world♪

240
00:13:06,180 --> 00:13:07,860
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

241
00:13:07,940 --> 00:13:09,300
♪My pride is my trump card♪

242
00:13:09,300 --> 00:13:11,060
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

243
00:13:11,140 --> 00:13:12,500
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

244
00:13:12,660 --> 00:13:14,380
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

245
00:13:14,380 --> 00:13:15,500
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

246
00:13:15,900 --> 00:13:17,540
♪I dare to break every rule♪

247
00:13:17,580 --> 00:13:18,860
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

248
00:13:18,860 --> 00:13:20,780
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

249
00:13:20,780 --> 00:13:21,900
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

250
00:13:21,900 --> 00:13:24,220
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

251
00:13:24,220 --> 00:13:25,740
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

252
00:13:25,740 --> 00:13:27,300
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

253
00:13:27,300 --> 00:13:29,060
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

254
00:13:29,060 --> 00:13:30,420
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

255
00:13:30,420 --> 00:13:32,340
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

256
00:13:32,340 --> 00:13:33,620
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

257
00:13:33,620 --> 00:13:35,300
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

258
00:13:35,300 --> 00:13:36,940
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

259
00:13:36,940 --> 00:13:38,620
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

260
00:13:38,660 --> 00:13:40,060
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

261
00:13:40,060 --> 00:13:41,580
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

262
00:13:41,740 --> 00:13:46,060
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

263
00:13:46,180 --> 00:13:48,060
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

264
00:13:48,140 --> 00:13:50,740
♪Let me write the legend♪

265
00:13:55,660 --> 00:13:58,060
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

266
00:13:58,260 --> 00:14:01,380
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

267
00:14:01,620 --> 00:14:04,020
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

268
00:14:04,020 --> 00:14:08,220
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

269
00:14:08,580 --> 00:14:11,180
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

270
00:14:11,300 --> 00:14:13,660
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

271
00:14:13,660 --> 00:14:16,700
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

272
00:14:16,700 --> 00:14:21,660
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
